cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper proposes a new network architecture for semantic segmentation, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed architecture involves multiple layers and connections, which are related to deep learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also reports experimental results on three datasets, which are related to multimedia (cs.MM).
